OL,7,Fat the Grammy Awards on Sunday.
OL,9,F"When I say I'm happy to be here, I
OL,10,Freally mean it from my heart," she
OL,11,Ftold the audience before announcing
OL,12,FTaylor Swift as the winner of album of
OL,13,Fthe year.
OL,15,F"Those who have been blessed enough to
OL,16,Fbe here at the Grammy Awards must
OL,17,Fnever take for granted the tremendous
OL,18,Flove and joy that music brings to our
OL,19,Flives and to people all around the
OL,20,Fworld."
