OL,6,FWhat is Stiff Person Syndrome?
OL,8,FSPS is a rare, progressive
OL,9,Fneurological disorder of the central
OL,10,Fnervous system and affects around one
OL,11,Fin a million people, according to the
OL,12,FNational Organization for Rare
OL,13,FDisorders (NORD).
OL,15,FIf left untreated it can lead to
OL,16,Fpermanent disability or death.
