OL,3,CWhat is the 'human statue' condition
OL,4,Cafflicting Celine Dion?
OL,6,FThe symptoms usually develop slowly
OL,7,Fover several months or years, often
OL,8,Fbeginning with muscle stiffness and
OL,9,Fdiscomfort which can come and go - but
OL,10,Fthe stiffness gradually becomes fixed.
OL,12,FSome develop a "statue-like"
OL,13,Fappearance due to the rigidity.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/8
