OL,3,CWhat is the 'human statue' condition
OL,4,Cafflicting Celine Dion?
OL,6,FMany also experience painful muscle
OL,7,Fspasms that can last a few minutes to
OL,8,Fseveral hours and may affect the whole
OL,9,Fbody or certain muscles. The spasms
OL,10,Fcan be triggered by unexpected loud
OL,11,Fnoises, minor physical contact, cold
OL,12,Fenvironments, stress, or situations
OL,13,Fthat cause heightened emotions, says
OL,14,Fthe NORD.
OL,16,FSpasms in the chest and respiratory
OL,17,Fmuscles can be serious and require
OL,18,Fventilation or emergency treatment,
OL,19,Fwhile spasms in the legs often lead to
OL,20,Ffalls.
