OL,3,CWhat is the 'human statue' condition
OL,4,Cafflicting Celine Dion?
OL,6,FExperts still do not know the exact
OL,7,Fcause of SPS and it is often
OL,8,Funderdiagnosed.
OL,10,FWho is affected by Stiff Person
OL,11,FSyndrome?
OL,13,FThe condition is twice as likely to
OL,14,Faffect females than males, according
OL,15,Fto the National Institute of
OL,16,FNeurological Disorders and Stroke.
OL,18,FIt is frequently associated with other
OL,19,Fautoimmune diseases such as type-I
OL,20,Fdiabetes, thyroiditis, vitiligo, and
OL,21,Fpernicious anemia.
