OL,3,CWhat is the 'human statue' condition
OL,4,Cafflicting Celine Dion?
OL,6,FThe condition only occurs in about one
OL,7,Fin every million people.JHow is Stiff
OL,8,FPerson Syndrome treated?
OL,10,FThere is no cure for SPS but
OL,11,Ftreatment, such as anti-seizure drugs,
OL,12,Fpainkillers and anti-anxiety
OL,13,Fmedication, can help lessen symptoms.
OL,15,FThe condition is thought to have
OL,16,Ffeatures of an autoimmune disease,
OL,17,Faccording to the National Institute of
OL,18,FNeurological Disorders and Stroke.
