OL,3,CWhat is the 'human statue' condition
OL,4,Cafflicting Celine Dion?
OL,6,FSeveral symptoms improve with anti-
OL,7,Fanxiety and muscle relaxant drugs, or
OL,8,Fwith drugs that alleviate muscle
OL,9,Fspasms, such as baclofen or gabapentin.
OL,11,FFor a singer like Dion, bright lights
OL,12,Fand loud noises that could occur while
OL,13,Fperforming could trigger muscle spasms.
